section_title: Compilation and Synthesis of Initial National Communications
sentences: The Secretariat noted inconclusive discussions at SBI 21 and COP 10 on guidance to the GEF on this issue (FCCC/SBI/2005/INF.2 and FCCC/SBI/2004/L.23).
Parties agreed to hold informal consultations.
